    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3573476>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Color morphs of Ophiothrix savignyi [SMNH-178933], Persian Gulf, Bustaneh. A, live photo, dorsal aspect, note the wide red line along the arms and the absence of dark border lines, B–E, same animal, preserved in ethanol, the brown disc is grey-blue, the red line is white, B, dorsal aspect, C, ventral aspect, D, dorsal arm, E, disc spines, F, live photo, dorsal aspect, along arms a narrower red line with thin dark borders, G, H, same animal, preserved in ethanol, the brown disc has changed to dark blue, the red line has turned white, G, dorsal aspect, H, dorsal arm, I, J, live photos, brown animal with white line along arms, bordered by thin blue lines, I, dorsal aspect, J, ventral aspect, K, L, same animal preserved in ethanol, brown has turned to blue." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3573476/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3573470>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Habitats at the sites where brittle stars were collected by the present study (see Table 1). A, Bandar Lengeh, B, Bustaneh, C, Chabahar Bay (Hotel Lipar), D, Chabahar Bay (University coast), E, Chabahar Bay (Tis), F, Qeshm Island." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3573470/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3573474>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Live photos of Ophiocomella sexradia [SMNH-178932], Persian Gulf, Qeshm Island. A, dorsal aspect, B, ventral aspect, C, dorsal disc, D, oral frame, E, dorsal arm, F, ventral arm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3573474/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

